text: Dusty, crowded, hot, stuffy, tight. Try not to transit here if you have the option not to.

The bus arrival timing displayed on Google for this bus stop is very inaccurate. At other bus stops, the timing is typically only 1-2 minutes off, but here, it's completely random. Depending on the bus timing, I could have found a different route to work, but instead, I'm left waiting for buses that I thought would arrive based on Google maps.
Makeshift bus stop with a few benches, however rain tends to get the benches wet making the shelter redundant.
